{"tid":243034,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"被捕4樂手眾籌6萬回港報到","createTime":"2017-05-14T11:11:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-15T10:05:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":21,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4552340401388f1872f5123aa1f75a7e1f9ea350","tid":243034,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:11:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20020889&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170514\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20020889%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170514&d=uMWHtpimsJ%2FyHBgDjrBiutibCDpHM%2Bj7ejEBwfn5qys%3D&h=b4bbc89a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D20020889%26category_guid%3D4104%26category%3Ddaily%26issue%3D20170514&h=a8e39172\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=20020889&amp;category_guid=4104&amp;category=daily&amp;issue=20170514</a><br />\n<br />\n被捕4樂手眾籌6萬回港報到<br />\n<br />\n要聞&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼&nbsp;￼<br />\n<br />\n￼<br />\n<br />\n被捕的4名英美音樂人當日於入境處協助調查。<br />\n<br />\n【HA風波】<br />\n有「獨立音樂界紅館」稱號的Hidden Agenda（HA）日前被執法部門打壓，連獲邀來港表演的英美樂隊成員也被捕，其中4人須於下月回港向警方報到。他們正在網上籌募合共約5萬元的來港旅費，現已達標。有香港樂迷更在網站留言，為香港政府對他們帶來的不便致歉。<br />\n<br />\n樂迷代表港府道歉<br />\n<br />\nHA日前邀請英國樂隊This Town Needs Guns（下稱：TTNG）及美國音樂人Mylets，於觀塘鴻圖道一工廠大廈單位表演時，遭入境處職員放蛇，指參與表演的外國樂隊違法演出，以欠工作簽證為由要扣留表演者，又指場地負責人涉請黑工，帶走相關人士。<br />\n遭入境處拘捕的4名音樂人獲保釋候查，並已離開香港，但須按保釋條件於6月5日回港報到。由於缺乏旅費，TTNG與Mylets透過籌款網站GoFundMe籌募旅費，他們目標是5,000英鎊（約5萬港元），獲得全球不少樂迷支持，截至昨晚11時半，已經達標籌得6.2萬港元。<br />\nTTNG成員獲准保釋後，曾於facebook留言多謝香港樂迷支持、多謝議員及律師團隊協助，並指：「這次特別的經歷，讓我們知道音樂工作者要在香港生存，原來那麼困難，需要有很大的熱情才能堅持下去。香港應該是一個自由多元的國際城市，有更大的空間鼓勵音樂創作和表演。」<br />\n事件引起國際關注，質疑香港警方及入境處以人力打壓音樂表演者，有大批香港樂迷於TTNG的fb留言以示支持，代表香港向他們道歉，更有人指為香港政府的行為蒙羞。<br />\n■記者劉書寧"},{"pid":"e334f7588487a75721d5d4b7e776e04aec0cc480","tid":243034,"uid":20227,"like":4,"dislike":13,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:26:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1df81928d69f3623414631f8ba0461f197e09047","tid":243034,"uid":43308,"like":4,"dislike":15,"score":-11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:27:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ad7473636597603133190017d3bbf68d40f3cefd","tid":243034,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:34:55.000Z","msg":"好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0042c17b624a6d8c8ac5a873d9f5ab7a2f3d49a","tid":243034,"uid":5320,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:35:55.000Z","msg":"上面有2件垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"94b3856785a933f1cd71856dcfd0b02bd0678671","tid":243034,"uid":56428,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:36:53.000Z","msg":"政府食屎啦"},{"pid":"0a8dfd5744c6b077a5d23b4d1b17ac367dd50ea0","tid":243034,"uid":62097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:37:37.000Z","msg":"兩隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ddbae0c077e1f4dbdc69baeeed4effb94efd9baf","tid":243034,"uid":57797,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:38:30.000Z","msg":"另類呃水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a50d42f47393557cda7236034c2a680dea786c71","tid":243034,"uid":39177,"like":1,"dislike":8,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:39:20.000Z","msg":"蠢鳩鬼佬,走數啦,我地中國人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"930742758701a4e82a84e51b09b1d9396465597e","tid":243034,"uid":20227,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T11:40:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7654135ed4812b925dc1e3c04e2c0e66b300adce","tid":243034,"uid":53026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-